HEADWORD: Lamellirostres
<hw>La*mel`li*ros"tres</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos>
<ety>[NL. See <er>Lamella</er>, and <er>Rostrum</er>.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A group of birds embracing the Anseres and
flamingoes, in which the bill is lamellate.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

